member.name: ISynchronizeHandle.GetHandle
member.summary: Retrieves a handle to the synchronization object.
member.param: A pointer to the variable that receives a handle to the synchronization object.
member.returns: This method can return the standard return values E_INVALIDARG, E_OUTOFMEMORY, E_FAIL, and S_OK.

member.name: ISynchronizeHandle
member.summary: Retrieves a handle associated with a synchronization object.
